# Tags and their uses 

1. <html> </html> : This contain all the data inside it.
2. <body> </body> : We can add data which can be shown into the website. 
3. <head> </head> : We can add data which works in the background. 
4. <title> </title> : For naming the website so user can identifie it.
5. <p> </p> : By this tag we can make multiple paragraphs. 
6. <h1> </h1> : This is the main heading and beside this there are 6 other headings form h1 to h6.
7. <storng> </strong> : This makes text bold.
8. <em> </em> : This makes text italic.



